# 🧑‍💻 Ishal Prishika Chand - Software Engineer Portfolio

Welcome to my personal software engineering portfolio! This web-based project highlights my professional background, skills, and projects. It is designed using modern frontend technologies like **HTML**, **CSS (TailwindCSS)**, and **Font Awesome**, with optional backend email functionality using **PHP**.

---

## 🌐 Live Demo

> 🚀 Coming soon: [https://yourdomain.com](https://yourdomain.com)

---

## 📁 Project Structure

```bash
/
├── home.html          # Main portfolio homepage
├── send_email.php      # Handles form submissions (PHP-enabled hosting only)
├── thankyou.html       # Confirmation page after form submission
├── img/                # Images used in the portfolio (projects, personal photo)
└── README.md           # This file

Features
✅ Responsive Design — Optimized for mobile, tablet, and desktop
🎨 TailwindCSS — Utility-first design for quick layout and style control
📬 Contact Form — Sends email via PHP or Formspree (configurable)
🧠 Projects Section — Showcases major academic and personal projects
🧾 Skills Matrix — Categorized technical skills for easy reference
📸 Hero Image & Profile Info — Highlights personal branding and bio

🛠 Technologies Used
HTML5
CSS3
TailwindCSS
Font Awesome
PHP — For handling contact form submissions
GitHub Pages — Deployment options
